To install:

type:
./configure
make
make install

Note.: The compilation is qmake based, not automake/autoconf based.

To run, type:
knetstats

Any doubts or suggestions, hugo_pl@users.sourceforge.net

To uninstall:

Type:
rm -f /usr/bin/knetstats
rm -rdf /usr/share/apps/knetstats/*
rm -f /usr/share/applications/knetstats.desktop
rm -f $HOME/.kde/share/config/knetstats.rc

--
Hugo P.L.